---
title: Persian-Style Chicken with Jeweled Rice Enjoy a multi-dish culinary tour of a new destination!
description: For this Persian-inspired dish, you'll marinate chicken in yogurt and warm spices, then sear it to juicy perfection. On the side, you'll serve basmati rice studded with tangy dried cherries and earthy pistachios, a fresh cucumber-tomato salad, and savory roasted veggies. Don't forget the hummus and tzatziki, which pair perfectly with warm pita!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67b2e2a7a27a53fcaa21ee03-05b7f880.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/67b2e2a7a27a53fcaa21ee03-en-US.pdf
nutrition:
